  "instructions": [
    "Wash and chop the spinach into bite-sized pieces.",
    "Heat olive oil in a wok or large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add minced garlic, cumin, chili powder, and salt to the hot pan. Stir for about 30 seconds until fragrant.",
    "Stir in the chopped spinach and cook until wilted, about 2 minutes.",
    "Pour in lime juice and stir well to combine flavors.",
    "Serve immediately while the spinach is still slightly steamed."
